# Construct Directory Structure

Construct is the standalone editor app (prop/actor builder). **Never** add editor logic to `viberanium/` or gameplay logic from `sandbox/`.

## Layout

```
construct/src/
├── ConstructApp.tsx        # package entry re-export only
├── catalog/                # documents, keys, manifest, document↔def converters
│   ├── actors/              # ActorDocument type + parse/serialize/convert
│   ├── props/               # PropDocument type + parse/serialize/convert
│   ├── keys/                # CONSTRUCT_KEYS component key strings
│   ├── manifest/            # KaykitManifest types, loader, tree filters, lookup helpers
│   └── slugify.ts            # shared document-id slugify helper
├── entities/                # factories, components, systems
│   ├── editorCommon/         # shared origin marker, colliders, editableTarget, TRS, materials
│   ├── actorEditor/          # actor root/character/attachment/collider spawn + systems
│   ├── propEditor/           # prop root/part spawn + systems
│   ├── gizmos/               # move/scale/rotate gizmo meshes, input, picking, system
│   ├── orbit/                # orbit camera + origin marker + anim preview entity
│   ├── viewer/                # standalone preview helpers (model bounds)
│   └── ground/               # spawnGround — editor ground plane
├── scenes/                  # editorScene load/unload + scaffold helpers
├── session/                 # preview, propEditor, actorEditor, anim session slices + types
├── globals/                 # bootstrap — thin composition only
├── storage/                 # localStore factory + actor/prop local store wrappers
└── ui/
    ├── app/                  # ConstructApp shell + useConstruct* hooks
    ├── explorer/             # AssetExplorer, Tree
    ├── inspector/             # PropInspector/ActorInspector, *Details, shared.tsx, euler
    ├── menu/                  # AppMenu (File menu, mode switch)
    ├── modals/                # Confirm/LoadProp/LoadActor/Rename/Tag modals
    ├── orientation/           # OrientationCube
    ├── viewer/                # ViewerAnimHud
    └── theme/                 # style.css
```

## Catalog rule

`catalog/` holds document types, parse/serialize, and manifest data — **no registry writes, no spawn logic**.

| Belongs in `catalog/` | Belongs outside `catalog/` |
|-----------------------|----------------------------|
| `PropDocument` / `ActorDocument` types + parse/serialize | `spawnPropEditor`, `spawnActorEditor` |
| `CONSTRUCT_KEYS` component key strings | `install*System` |
| `KaykitManifest` types, `loadKaykitManifest`, tree filters | `bootstrap` composition |
| Document ↔ `PropDefinition`/`ActorDefinition` converters | Session slices (`session/*`) |
| `slugifyDocumentId` | UI hooks, React components |

**`catalog/` must not import from `entities/`, `session/`, `scenes/`, `globals/`, or `ui/`.**

## Entity rule

| Folder | Role |
|--------|------|
| `entities/editorCommon/` | Shared mechanics: origin marker, collider shape resources, `editableTarget`, `editorSelection`, materials, TRS, `syncPartLocal` |
| `entities/actorEditor/` | Actor root/character/attachment/collider components + `spawnActor*` + `installActorColliderFollowSystem` |
| `entities/propEditor/` | Prop root/part components + `spawnAssetPart`/`spawnColliderPart`/`spawnPropEditor` |
| `entities/gizmos/` | Move/scale/rotate gizmo meshes, picking, input, `installConstructGizmoSystem` |
| `entities/orbit/` | Orbit camera state, origin marker, anim preview entity, `installConstructOrbitSystem` |

Shared editor mechanics (used by both prop and actor editors) live in `entities/editorCommon/` — never duplicate origin marker, collider, or TRS logic per-editor.

## Session rule

- `session/types.ts` — `ConstructSession`, `ConstructSessionState`, `ConstructSessionDeps` types + `createConstructSessionState`
- `session/preview.ts` — standalone asset preview load/texture-variant slice
- `session/propEditor.ts` — prop document mutation slice (add/remove/rename/update parts)
- `session/actorEditor.ts` — actor document mutation slice (character/attachments/colliders)
- `session/anim.ts` — animation pack load/apply/clear slice

Session slices are pure functions of `(deps, state, ...)` returning updated documents — no React, no JSX.

## Globals rule

`globals/bootstrap.ts` composes engine primitives (render pipeline, orbit, gizmos, systems) into a `ConstructSession` — composition only, no document mutation logic (that lives in `session/`).

## Storage rule

- `storage/localStore.ts` — generic `createLocalStore<TDoc>(storageKey)` factory (list/get/save/remove)
- `storage/actorLocalStore.ts` / `storage/propLocalStore.ts` — thin wrappers binding the factory to `ActorDocument`/`PropDocument` with a storage-clone function

Do not reimplement read/write/list/remove localStorage logic per document type — extend `localStore.ts`.

## UI rule

- `ui/app/ConstructApp.tsx` — layout shell only: panels, modals wiring, mode switch UI. Delegates lifecycle and workflow logic to `ui/app/useConstruct*.ts` hooks
- `ui/app/useConstructSession.ts` — bootstrap lifecycle, session ref, prop/actor document state + listeners
- `ui/app/useManifestExplorer.ts` — manifest load, asset/character trees, explorer search + expand state
- `ui/app/useConstructViewer.ts` — preview model loading, texture variant + animation preview state
- `ui/app/useConstructMode.ts` — mode + transform-mode state, tab-cycle input, enter-prop/actor-mode effect
- `ui/app/useConstructSelection.ts` — selected prop part / actor selection state
- `ui/app/useConstructDocumentActions.ts` — New/Save/Load/Import/Export/Rename workflows + modals
- `ui/app/useConstructAssetActions.ts` — add asset/character/collider from the explorer
- `ui/app/useConstructInspectorActions.ts` — per-field edit handlers wired into `PropDetails`/`ActorDetails`
- UI talks only to `ConstructSession` (via `bootstrap`) or catalog document helpers — **never import `entities/` from `ui/`**
- `ui/inspector/shared.tsx` — shared `AxisRow`, `DetailsHeader`, `formatNum`/`parseNum` for `PropDetails`/`ActorDetails`

## Forbidden

- Barrel `index.ts` anywhere under `construct/src/`
- Comments in agent-generated `.ts`/`.tsx` source
- God objects in `globals/bootstrap.ts` or `ui/app/ConstructApp.tsx` — one concern per file/hook
- Component key strings outside `catalog/keys/components.ts`
- Duplicated `AxisRow`/`formatNum`/`parseNum`/rename-header JSX across inspector panels — use `ui/inspector/shared.tsx`
- Duplicated localStorage read/write/list/remove logic across `storage/*LocalStore.ts` — use `storage/localStore.ts`
- `entities/` imports from `ui/`
